messageBody:
--- In Read_Alphabet@yahoogroups.com, Michael Everson <everson@...> wrote:

> I don't believe so. I sent a file called "Screen Shot 2012-12-31 at 10.31.06.png"
[...]
> All I sent was a screen shot .png taken of the page as loaded in Safari.

Wow. This is WAY too weird. I'm about ready to chalk this up to yet another Poe mystery and leave it at that. :-) Can you at least view the picture that I uploaded to the files section OK? That's what came through in the private e-mail that showed up. I also can't help but wonder, is there anyone out there who can actually see stuff on my home page other than a huge mass of black? Is there anyone out there who, like me, sees the text and the 2 book covers? This is really starting to worry me. It won't be of any help at all if I'm the only one in the world that can see it properly, especially if there's absolutely no logical explanation for why this should be so...
